import React, { useState, useEffect, useContext } from "react";
import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"
import { Context } from "../../servicos/context"

import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'
import { faPlus, faTrash } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'

const Principal = () => {

  const [message, setMessage] = useState("Hello World");
  const informations = useContext(Context)

  useEffect(() => { console.log(informations) }, [])

  return (
    <Container style={{ fontFamily: "Courier New" }}>

      <Row>
        <Col style={{ fontSize: 36, color: "#95AF5F", }}>Bem-vindo, {informations.infos.name}!</Col>
      </Row>

      <Row md={4} style={{ marginTop: 50 }} noGutters>
        <Col md={2}><FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPlus} style={{ border: "solid", borderRadius:50 }} /></Col>
        <Col md={2}><FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTrash} /></Col>
      </Row>

      <Row md={12} style={{ width: "20%", height: "80%", border: "solid", borderColor: "black", borderWidth: "1px", borderRadius: 3, padding: 12 }}>
        <Row>
          <Col>Ol√°</Col>
        </Row>

      </Row>

    </Container>
  )

}

export default Principal;
